Title from caption and first lines of text. At end: "By Rich Collins, from nine to twelve ..." Imprint from Wing. Order to print at foot: "Printed with consent of the president, and censors of the College of Physicians, in London." Imperfect: slight loss of print. Reproduction of original in the British Library.
